data.description: No more carrying groceries and laundry up flights of stairs..Long time owner is ready to sell! This 2BR/2BA ground level condo, is in fantastic condition. New windows in 2019, new Hot water heater, newer A/C, and in-unit laundry. This South facing condo has lots of natural light and the open layout is just another added bonus to go with the huge master bathroom and walk-in closet. Close to shopping, main streets, grocery stores, and the gated entry gives you added reassurance. Schedule your showing, it's Ready to sell..(For sale only, Unit is not for rent)
